        "content": "<p>alexcrichton opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13002\">PR #13002</a> from <code>alexcrichton:ghsa-backports-24</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:release-24.0.0</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fixes included:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Out-of-bounds write or crash when transcoding component model strings.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/security/advisories/GHSA-394w-hwhg-8vgm\">GHSA-394w-hwhg-8vgm</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Wasmtime segfault or unused out-of-sandbox load with <code>f64x2.splat</code> operator<br>\n  on x86-64.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/security/advisories/GHSA-qqfj-4vcm-26hv\">GHSA-qqfj-4vcm-26hv</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Panic when transcoding misaligned utf-16 strings.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/security/advisories/GHSA-jxhv-7h78-9775\">GHSA-jxhv-7h78-9775</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Panic when lifting <code>flags</code> component value.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/security/advisories/GHSA-m758-wjhj-p3jq\">GHSA-m758-wjhj-p3jq</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Heap OOB read in component model UTF-16 to latin1+utf16 string transcoding.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/security/advisories/GHSA-hx6p-xpx3-jvvv\">GHSA-hx6p-xpx3-jvvv</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
